request.description:
This mutation will take in an **input** object and update one **OR** many fields on an individual customer.

Update customer requires a very simple input object that can be expanded upon:

``` json
{
    "channel": "SALESFORCE", // client channel
    "userPulseId": "rz28v6", // user id
    "suppressCustomerCommunication": false,
    "requestPayload": {
      "partyType": "Individual",
      "individual": {    // the individual is where fields to be updated will live
        "altIdList": [   // altIdList needs only one ID to identify a customer
          {              // this is the customer to be updated
            "type": "ACM",
            "value": "294265300836794502",
            "dataProvider": true
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }

```

